{"tid":190672,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［陰毛撚］我對於連登比5p mk入侵既睇法","createTime":"2017-04-07T09:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T19:21:40.000Z","uid":11080,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0adb5c81ead74c34ea2c836df574a766fa641fa5","tid":190672,"uid":11080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"咁小弟都上左高登+連登大約10年 都叫做睇過呢到既轉變<br />\n<br />\n基於琴日有個熱門post係講連登越黎越低質，有感而法<br />\n<br />\n當初連登account係開比:<br />\n1. Isp email登記<br />\n2. Lihkg vip用戶<br />\n<br />\n咁好明顯係lihkg vip用戶出事啦，因為高登用左（1）咁多年都相安無事。<br />\n<br />\n但係連仔其實又冇做錯到，話哂lihkg同連登都係佢同團體既心血結晶，所以首先唔可以怪佢地<br />\n<br />\n不過就係因為（2）搞到好多小學雞mk 5p都入到黎留言 講埋d吾系甘牙，仲屌返人轉頭，我自己都覺得好討厭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以下為重點</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5e13eeb80ac570c94a063b5ed7e13225e88742","tid":190672,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"清岩牙👍"},{"pid":"96b836be3a4b9083ca753f50facf2ae6048657dd","tid":190672,"uid":11080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清岩牙👍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉屌打左咁多野最重要個回覆會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f6346c63956ca40279e1b3ebe66346e4a5bdfb","tid":190672,"uid":45505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:38:14.000Z","msg":"千錯萬錯都係joe仔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8988d75d76c2bf2d4fd3654b311ab82f79442ae9","tid":190672,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清岩牙👍</blockquote><br />\n你老母俾狗屌"},{"pid":"8fc8c786106844cbe4369770f7145af616e9e491","tid":190672,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB